{
  "stem": "11205.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was really-- you know, I felt that I was not-- not alone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were-- then I start to look for work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it just happen-- also, I want to mention when we were working together with my sister, she-- she developed a terrible cough--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Tomsk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the work was quite very far up the hill.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at that time, if you are late for work, they take a-- 20%, like, from your wages.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so she developed such a cough on the way to work that she-- and here the sirens started that-- to-- already to be at work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I couldn't leave her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was blue.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I couldn't leave her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she told me, you run, because they wouldn't believe us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came to work, and I was worried what happened to her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually, maybe half an hour later, she came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came there also because we-- we were afraid they will-- it was a big prosecution, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did-- did--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why when I-- my brother-in-law send me-- sent for me, I ran away from work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't know what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was not legal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't had a ticket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He paid the woman which was the conductor of that wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She-- one day she came to work, and she gave me a letter written in Yiddish that-- to-- to go to this address to this woman and to talk over.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She will tell me all-- what it is about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was mobilizing, but he had a good job in the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was working in the-- where they repair shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- it wasn't his profession, but it was a big privilege in Siberia to be near shoes or near bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
